al-khawf","tag-god-fearing-taqwa","tag-supplication-of-oppressed-dawah-al-mazlum","tag-supplication-al-dua","tag-warning-al-nudhr","tag-wrongdoing-al-thulm"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9oy","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":27524,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/11\/dua-oppressed-answered\/","url_meta":{"origin":36118,"position":0},"title":"Umar on Injustice: Supplication of oppressed always answered","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aslam reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, appointed a client of his named Hunayy to tend the pasture, saying, \u201cO Hunayy, lower your wing for the Muslims and beware the supplication of the oppressed, for the supplication of the oppressed is answered.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3059\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":359,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/01\/08\/priorities-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":36118,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dawah: Priorities of Islam are faith, prayer, charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 8, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu'adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, sent me to Yemen\u00a0and he said, \u201cVerily, you are going to people among the people of the Book, so call them to testify there is no God but Allah and I am the Messenger of Allah.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5257,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/18\/three-dua-never-rejected\/","url_meta":{"origin":36118,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Three supplications always answered","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThree supplications are answered without a doubt: the supplication of an oppressed person, the supplication of a traveler, and the supplication of a parent over his child.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1905 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23205,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/06\/14\/dua-oppressed-answered-2\/","url_meta":{"origin":36118,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication of oppressed eventually answered","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Khuzaymah ibn Thabit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBeware of the supplication of the oppressed, for it is carried above the clouds. Allah Almighty says: By My might and majesty, I will help you in due time.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 3718 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_t